    <string name="howtouse" >
        When you install the app, make sure that your phone sensor is working so that it can track your steps correctly.
        \nThe timer in the app will assess your walking time and calories will help you to assess the calories you burnt.
        \nAlongwith it you can also set your health goals.
    </string>

    <string name="counting_when_shaking_phn" >
       If you shake your phone it might be counted as steps because of the built-in-sensor.It is not a bug.
    </string>

    <string name="accuracy" >
       We use built-in-sensor in your phone to count your steps,so the accuracy is based on how good the sensor is.
    </string>

    <string name="placement_sugg" >
       Put your phone in your hand,pocket,bag,armband or places close to your body. \nDo not put your phone in places away from your body or
        places that shakes too fast.
    </string>

    <string name="cal_dist" >
       We use your height,weight and age information to calculate the total calories burnt.
        \nThe total distance covered is calculated automatically by using the count of steps.
        \nPlease fill in the information correctly at the time of registration or you can also edit them through edit profile option.
    </string>

    <string name="privacy_str" >
